Destinations

GeoEx offers a sensationally varied roster of cultural tours, treks, safaris, and journeys by train and ship to the world's most astonishing places. We're passionate about tending to your wanderlust with expertly designed small-group trips and individually crafted custom journeys to the ends of the earth.




