 Blue Man Group 
The avant-garde Blue Man Group combines theatrics, art, music and science to create an interactive, percussion-driven experience full of humor and energy. 


 "O" by Cirque du Soleil ® 
Cirque du Soleil paints an aquatic masterpiece of surrealism and theatrical romance in the timeless production, “O.” 


