Allegiant Air is an American low-cost airline that operates scheduled and charter flights. It is wholly owned by Allegiant Travel Company (NASDAQ: ALGT), a publicly traded company with 3,700 employees and over $2.6 billion USD market capitalization.[7] The corporate headquarters are in Summerlin, Nevada, a suburb of Las Vegas.[8]



