Allegiant Travel Reaches Analyst Target Price
In recent trading, shares of Allegiant Travel Company have crossed above the average analyst 12-month target price of $179.50, changing hands for $180.40/share. When a stock reaches the target an analyst has set, the analyst logically has two ways to react: downgrade on valuation, or, re-adjust their target price to a higher level.

