        Contact Us


Whether it's a general inquiry or a specific question about an upcoming trip, we'd like to hear from you. Please give us a call, use this form, or e-mail us at [email protected].

Telephone & Fax
Tel: 888-570-7108 or 415-922-0448
Fax: 415-346-5535 
Business Hours
Monday–Friday, 8:00 a.m.–5:00 p.m. (Pacific time)
Address & Directions:
Geographic Expeditions
1008 General Kennedy Avenue
PO Box 29902
San Francisco, CA, 94129-0902, USA
Directions to our office
On-Trip Emergency Contact Information:
If you need help during off-business hours while you are traveling, contact Global Rescue, our emergency assistance provider (staffed 24/7 and in touch with GeoEx staff) by calling 800-381-9754 (from North America) or 617-459-4200 (collect calls accepted), or by e-mailing [email protected]. 







