Information about Allegiant Air
 When you travel on Allegiant Air flights, you can expect:Budget friendly travelThe ability to fly to various cities throughout the USEase of booking through the company's website
Get the cheapest Allegiant Air flights on JetcostThis is an airline that specializes in national flights within the US. The most popular destinations for Allegiant Air flights include Orlando, Las Vegas and Tampa, with Phoenix and Los Angeles also pretty high up on the list.  The reason that Allegiant Air tickets are so budget friendly is that the airline maintains strict control over its pricing policies. You can only purchase tickets for Allegiant Air flights via the Allegiant Air website. This prevents other companies trying to undercut or inflate its ticket prices. The airline also often offers limited time only cut price deals on many of its tickets which makes travelling with them even cheaper than usual.  If you are looking for a cheap way to travel within the US, then this could very well be the perfect airline for you. Whether you are planning on taking flights to United States for business or for pleasure, you will be sure to be able to find a flight with this airline that is convenient for your plans. When it comes to the most popular destination of Orland, for example, this airline operates 115 flights per week. 
