                    Allegiant Air
                                        (G4/AAY)
                                        

 Headquartered in Nevada, Allegiant Air offers low cost air travel. This airline provides both scheduled flights and charter flights. Charter flights have carried everyone from politicians to US baseball teams. With its slogan 'travel is our deal', Allegiant Air announces its commitment to helping passengers to find the best deal for them when it comes to travelling by air. 






